# Strategic Strategy: Modularize & Audit (Build 1101E)

This plan shifts our focus to **Modularization (Refactoring)** as the primary priority. By splitting large files into smaller, focused modules, we reduce "Context Noise" and allow AI agents (like Opus 4.6) to perform deeper forensic audits with higher accuracy.

## Proposed Changes

### [Phase 1: UI Modularization] [COMPLETED]
Split [UniversalORStrategyV12_002_Dev.UI.cs](file:///C:/WSGTA/universal-or-strategy/src/UniversalORStrategyV12_002_Dev.UI.cs) (~2246 lines) into:
- [UI.IPC.cs](file:///C:/WSGTA/universal-or-strategy/src/UniversalORStrategyV12_002_Dev.UI.IPC.cs): TCP Server, Client Handlers, and `ProcessIpcCommands`.
- [UI.Compliance.cs](file:///C:/WSGTA/universal-or-strategy/src/UniversalORStrategyV12_002_Dev.UI.Compliance.cs): Compliance Hub, P/L tracking, and Daily Summary logic.
- [UI.Sizing.cs](file:///C:/WSGTA/universal-or-strategy/src/UniversalORStrategyV12_002_Dev.UI.Sizing.cs): ATR Auto-Sizing Engine and Position Sizing math.
- [UI.Callbacks.cs](file:///C:/WSGTA/universal-or-strategy/src/UniversalORStrategyV12_002_Dev.UI.Callbacks.cs): Hotkeys and Chart Click handlers.

### [Phase 2: Order Modularization] [COMPLETED]
Split [UniversalORStrategyV12_002_Dev.Orders.cs](file:///C:/WSGTA/universal-or-strategy/src/UniversalORStrategyV12_002_Dev.Orders.cs) (~2024 lines) into:
- [Orders.Callbacks.cs](file:///C:/WSGTA/universal-or-strategy/src/UniversalORStrategyV12_002_Dev.Orders.Callbacks.cs): `OnOrderUpdate`, `OnPositionUpdate`, and `OnAccountOrderUpdate`.
- [Orders.Management.cs](file:///C:/WSGTA/universal-or-strategy/src/UniversalORStrategyV12_002_Dev.Orders.Management.cs): `SubmitBracketOrders`, `CleanupPosition`, and `ReconcileOrphanedOrders`.
- `Orders.Actions.cs`: Hotkey execution logic (ExecuteLong, ExecuteShort, Flatten).

## Verification Plan

### Automated Verification
- **Compilation Check**: Run `F5` in NinjaTrader after each module split to ensure namespaces and `partial class` references are intact.

### Manual Verification
- **Agent Audit**: Hand one small module (e.g., [UI.Sizing.cs](file:///C:/WSGTA/universal-or-strategy/src/UniversalORStrategyV12_002_Dev.UI.Sizing.cs)) to **Opus 4.6** and ask it to find edge cases.
- **Result**: Compare finding density before vs. after refactor.
